title: Bruce Springsteen 1981-05-03 Gothenburg SWE

Here is another nice bootleg recording. Check my account for more classic bootlegs.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)

This upload is part of the Riverflood project.

This Upload will include an infofile, logfiles, checksum,
